{"title":"和平的长城——献给十月","authors":["甘永柏"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给十月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘永柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个明朗的五月的早晨，我在瓦杜丁将军〔一〕墓前脱下了自己的帽子。我感到深重的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉哀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有无比的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钦敬！阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水一般地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲洗着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基辅，市街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水晶似的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明。德聂伯河呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您悠悠的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水流，映照着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄壮的姿影！多少思潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澎湃在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的脑海，而最先使我想起的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争！因为我在想着瓦杜丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想着他所代表的千千万万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血，培育了这座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如花似锦的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的名城！呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平，四十年间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这英雄的国土打下了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少深刻的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烙印！为了把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远结束，而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将像败叶似地埋入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逝水；苏维埃呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又歌唱，甚至献出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最珍贵的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命。我背诵着马雅可夫斯基的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最高的敬礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给瓦杜丁将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一切为了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慷慨赴难的苏维埃人——“同志们，静静地安息吧……你们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年少的国家，随着每一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得更为光辉灿烂，它有力而又雄壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天天地巩固起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来”。〔二〕巩固起来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不只是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃的国土，全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善良的人民环绕着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼！一九五六年十一月，当你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵入埃及的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁蹄，又斩断了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们兄弟国家匈牙利的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔手，我在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国南方的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"港口看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人噙着眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤苏维埃的名字！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们是从孟买、长崎、开罗来的，他们是从利物浦、马赛、那不勒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯来的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们是从奥斯坦德、海参崴、革"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但斯克来的……他们欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公海上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新扬起和平的旗帜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将拥抱自己的家园！光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫和平的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民！光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔一〕瓦杜丁将军是苏联卫国战争中收复基辅的名将，在追击希特勒匪军的战役中牺牲，葬于基辅城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔二〕马雅可夫斯基长诗“好”第十八章中的句子。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}